**System Information (please complete the following information):**
 - OS & Version: Windows11 Pro 23H2 64GB
 - ML.NET Version: ML.NET 3.0.1
 - .NET Version: .NET 8.0

**Describe the bug**
Writing windows form application using ML.NET 3.0.1:

NuGet
Microsoft.ML Version 3.0.1
Microsoft.ML.AutoML Version 0.20.1
Microsoft.ML.CpuMath Version 3.0.1
Microsoft.ML.DataView Version 3.0.1
