Microsoft.ML.Mkl.Components Version 3.0.1
Microsoft.ML.Mkl.Redist Version 3.0.1

**To Reproduce**
Installing Microsoft.ML.AutoML Version 0.21.0 or 0.21.1, my Monitor class does not behave the way it does with Microsoft.ML.AutoML Version 0.20.1.

